  <h2 class="paragraph-title"> <b>Gift wrapping and packaging</b> </h2>
  <p class="paragraph">
  All orders come in custom Kokomi branded packaging which includes a unique box and drawstring bag. I always include little handwritten personalized notes and my 
  business card as well. What is the uncoated vs. coated cap option?
  </p>
  <p class="paragraph">
  I try to be inclusive of all admirers and potential customers and recognize that some may have metal sensitivities or allergies. The pendant caps are electroplated
  copper which can sometimes irritate especially sensitive skin. Larger pendants rarely touch the skin, but as a precautionary measure I give the option to request a 
  special protective coating for the cap. 
  </p>
  <p class="paragraph">
