  <h2 class="paragraph-title"> <b>Are these pendants safe for children?</b> </h2>
  <p class="paragraph">
  Generally speaking, my answer is no. I like dainty jewelry and as a result these pose a choking hazard.
  As I mentioned in the care instructions, the outside of my pieces are made of glass and are thus fragile and should be handled with care.
  </p>
  
  <h2 class="paragraph-title"> <b>What is AB glass?</b> </h2>
  <p class="paragraph">
  AB glass is a type of glass with an iridescent coating that essentially gives off rainbows in different lighting and angles.
  </p>

  <h2 class="paragraph-title"> <b>Can these pendants be used for keychains or pet collars?</b> </h2>
